{"tid":15904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個 娘娘送過最難忘既禮物","createTime":"2016-12-01T08:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T10:00:26.000Z","uid":42694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e765215d0985226d383fc4c227cc6e23c20c984a","tid":15904,"uid":42694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"年少無知 誤入兵營<br />\n行軍兩年某聖誕 <br />\n娘娘送左條<span style=\"color: red;\">好粗好長好黑既假九</span>比我<br />\n小弟菊花一緊 呑左啖囗水問佢送比我做乜<br />\n佢叫我收聲之後用條鳩鞭左我一野再拖我入房.....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02479dfd5b8c17aa2742ba00ce93e55d2e3c2550","tid":15904,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c43f85f08ae818234e29f8bd42719a1f5695d8b","tid":15904,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:11:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"910dbd46f8f86b76e31083291a4fe5f80dc0259a","tid":15904,"uid":42694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加甜，thx</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只能講 黑鬼遇上牛肺 黑媽媽乜都見唔到<br />\n<strong>重點</strong>佢唔比我掂 我只係佢個觀眾<br />\nDKLMCH<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ead737ee7e7eb597c2ee606bd68e5f305dfc0a","tid":15904,"uid":42694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"兵呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出來推一推"}]}